 @Produces(value="application/json")
 @Path(value="/list")
public ListStatusResult list(@FormParam(value="uuid")
                                                                                              java.lang.String uuid,
                                                                                              @FormParam(value="project")
                                                                                              java.lang.String project,
                                                                                              @FormParam(value="from")
                                                                                              java.lang.String from,
                                                                                              @FormParam(value="to")
                                                                                              java.lang.String to)
        Lists all results in a given period
        Parameters:
        uuid - Universally unique identifier of the user.
        project - A project owned by the user.
        from - (optional) The minimum start date of the job, or null for dates from any period. The used format is 'yyyyMMdd'
        to - (optional) The maximum start date of the job, or null for dates to any period. The used format is 'yyyyMMdd'
        Returns:
        A result containing the list of statuses and the code of the result.
        - RESTResultCodes.USER_NOT_AUTHORIZED if the user is not valid;
        - RESTResultCodes.USER_ERROR if the format of one the dates(from or to) is not null and is incorrect;
        - RESTResultCodes.OK if success;
        - RESTResultCodes.INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR if some error occurs.
